{
  "stem": "8703.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they became, you know, very intelligent, and all these things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would like to say one more thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I graduated Polish school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had younger brothers and sisters from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a very busy man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was my job to take care at the other children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six other children that I was responsible-- and I encourage because I knew all the teachers from before, when I was graduated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they all went to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were good students, the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- even, it came to, sometimes, to a problem, that if somebody did something wrong, they didn't say, wait till the daddy will come home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, wait till Israel will come home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then you'll see-- if they-- if they did something wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I thank God they were raised, and they went to school, and they were good students, all six younger kids from me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we was-- our social life was separate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Polish had a separate social life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had, also, contacts, of course, with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever we used to live, we had Polish neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But socialize, we did only with our own Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly-- yes, we had also Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the chauffeur was Polish, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The partner he had once-- he had once a partner, Polish partner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very friendly, no problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a problem while I was in school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a pogrom in Przytyk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Jewish people, at that time, all over Poland, were very, very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] aggravated about that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to do some work to complete some, some assignment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wrote about this pogrom in Przytyk.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
